David Adeleke, best known by his stage name Davido, is a prominent Nigerian artist who recently sparked mixed reactions among his followers and Instagram users after he posted a video of himself arriving in luxury in North Carolina, United States via his official verified Instagram account. In the video, the popular Nigerian musician is welcomed by his American friend, Neo, who was sighted at the airport alongside his music team shortly after his arrival.
Recall that, a few weeks ago, the Nigerian singer, hosted the American rapper, Dababy, who is a native of North Carolina. He reportedly came to Nigeria to work on a music video with afrobeat superstar, Davido.
While using the world’s largest photo-sharing app, to release the video for the viewing pleasure of his fans and well-wishers, he captioned the post with the following question;
“Ready?”
